001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 63,
011    displayName = "Tubing Filled",
012    usedByTidepool = true
013)
014public class TubingFilledHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    private float primeSize;
017    
018    public TubingFilledHistoryLog() {}
019    public TubingFilledHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, float primeSize) {
020        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
021        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, primeSize);
022        this.primeSize = primeSize;
023        
024    }
025
026    public TubingFilledHistoryLog(float primeSize) {
027        this(0, 0, primeSize);
028    }
029
030    public int typeId() {
031        return 63;
032    }
033
034    /**
035     * <table border="1">
036     * <caption>Parsed fields for TubingFilledHistoryLog:</caption>
037     * <tr><td><code>primeSize</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
038     * </table>
039     */
040    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
041        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
042        this.cargo = raw;
043        parseBase(raw);
044        this.primeSize = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 10);
045        
046    }
047
048    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, float primeSize) {
049        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
050            new byte[]{63, 0},
051            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
052            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
053            Bytes.toFloat(primeSize)));
054    }
055
056    /**
057     * @return the number of units used to prime the tubing
058     */
059    public float getPrimeSize() {
060        return primeSize;
061    }
062    
063}
